307
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:07,400
Okay.

308
00:15:09,570 --> 00:15:10,640
What do you think?

309
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,720
Is it weird?

310
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:16,100
If a regular person looks like a model,

311
00:15:16,170 --> 00:15:17,540
