312
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,400
Because it's like you're imitating others.

313
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,990
You did a great job.

314
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,270
You mean

315
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:25,080
